OL,3,CWoman died after getting trapped in
OL,4,Cfaulty ottoman bed
OL,6,FA coroner has issued a warning
OL,7,Ffollowing the death of a woman whose
OL,8,Fneck became trapped in a faulty
OL,9,Fottoman-style bed.
OL,11,FHelen Davey, 39 from Seaham, County
OL,12,FDurham, was "unable to free herself"
OL,13,Fwhen the raised mattress platform
OL,14,Fsuddenly fell, trapping her neck
OL,15,Fagainst the base of the bed on 7 June.
OL,17,FAn inquest into the beautician's death
OL,18,Ffound that one of the gas-lift
OL,19,Fpistons, which raise the mattress, was
OL,20,Fdefective - her death was recorded as
OL,21,Fan accident.
