OL,3,CWoman died after getting trapped in
OL,4,Cfaulty ottoman bed
OL,6,FFollowing the inquest Durham and
OL,7,FDarlington's senior coroner, Jeremy
OL,8,FChipperfield, has written to the the
OL,9,FBusiness Secretary and the Office for
OL,10,FProduct Safety and Standards calling
OL,11,Ffor action to prevent future deaths
OL,12,Frelating to failing mechanisms.
OL,14,FIn his report, Mr Chipperfield said:
OL,15,F"The deceased was leaning over the
OL,16,Fstorage area of an ottoman-styled 'gas-
OL,17,Flift bed' when the mattress platform
OL,18,Fdescended unexpectedly, trapping her
OL,19,Fneck against the upper surface of the
OL,20,Fside panel of the bed's base.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/4
