OL,6,FMr Chipperfield said it was his duty
OL,7,Fto raise concerns with the Office for
OL,8,FProduct Safety and Standards and the
OL,9,FDepartment for Business and Trade
OL,10,Fabout "the existence and use of gas
OL,11,Fpiston bed mechanisms whose failure
OL,12,Fpresents risk to life."
OL,14,FHe added: "In my opinion action should
OL,15,Fbe taken to prevent future deaths and
OL,16,FI believe you have the power to take
OL,17,Fsuch action."
